title: GONG STICKS IN THE PARK with Drew Sinclair
description: Gong Sticks  is a joyful, body-mind practice from the Tai Chi Health System. The 16 Mindful Movements are supported by a bamboo cane for stability and fluidity. Improves joint strength & flexibility, stress & emotions, and mental clarity.    Just turn  in comfy clothes and we'll provide the bamboo.
